Heavenly Gyu Tan Don at @mamagoosejkt! Accompanied by a slow poached egg on top, this menu is something you must eat before you die! Jl. Panglima Polim IX no.16
The New Balance X Shelflife X Dr.Z ML574CG "City Of Gold" edition. Thoughts? Available worldwide at @end_clothing soon!

The line today at @ronslaboratory Grand Indonesia was so long it blocked the escalator. But for a taste of the @puyodesserts X @ronslaboratory 's bubblegum gelato, it was worth queing! Get it fast while it's still available folks!
On behalf of @thrusociety , we wish you a Happy Easter and a Happy Sunday!

Repost from @charlotteroselim ! Another nitrogen ice cream sensation by @freezeindonesia. Their iconic pop up cone makes it hard to miss, especially their Green Tea Devil! Visit them at PIM or Mall Taman Anggrek!
Earth day is coming up people! Post a pic that promotes or helps our beloved Earth and get a chance to get a shoutout! Tag us or mention us @thrusociety

@casakemang is a place must visit if you are at Kemang. Their place has the perfect chill ambience and an array of wines. You should try their salmon because it is just out of this world! Jl. Kemang Raya no.8b
Looking for great and affordable Japanese fusion food? Headout to @tokyobelly at Grand Indonesia ASAP! You must try their mouth warering belly pao and wasabi bulgogi beef for sure!

Pomade is an essential to look dapper but if you're looking for a hairslick that doesn't feel like it's pulling your hair from it's roots, try Murray's NuNile! Their milky scent and average grip is the key to comfort and dapper looks. Available by order at @greasenhold or at stores at @standarddenim ! More info on them? Mention us at @thrusociety

caption.text: A new eclectic style gastropub/cafe/bistro has arrived at Bogor! @monarchybistro is a great place to hangout and get drinks with your friends and folks! For their food, their steaks are simply mesmerizing. Visit them at Jl.padjajaran indah 5!
Nike Airmax 90 by @nikesportswear is available at the @goodsdeptonline and @thegoodsdept! The lunar airmax 90 is available as well! Like em? Cop them fast!

Craving for a bowl of delicious ramen but afraid if it's not kosher? Have no fear! Visit Marutama ramen at Plaza Ex! Their amazing toritaipan broth is made out of 100% pure chicken and you must try their award winning aji tamago for sure. But if you want some pork on your ramen, you can order the pork kakuni or pork chashiu included ramen.

Captain America: The Winter Soldier is the must watch movie of the month! The story is about SHEILD being compromised by an old enemy and Steve Rogers (Chris Evans) facing an old friend who has become a weapon for the foe. The best part is that a new marvel hero emerges in this movie! Don't miss out people!

When the waiter comes at your table with a pot filled with dirt and worms you would probably get disgusted. But not at @hydekemang! Their chocolate soil dessert consists of worms and dirts made out of great chocolate! Interested? Try their unique concept  at Jl. Taman kemang 1A no.8, South Jakarta.

data.full_name: C H E R R I E

caption.text: Confused of where are you going to go this friday night? Why should be when there is a place like HYDE? A gastropub with a nostalgic ambience yet still shows that nightlife soul. You should try their Chocolate Soil and their "sip and go naked" cocktail! Jl. Taman Kemang 1A no.8, South Jakarta.

Kickstart your day with an authentic Indonesian coffee experience. Anomali Coffee serves coffee brewed from coffee beans from the various regions in Indonesia! Visit them at their very own coffee roasting facility, cafe and training facility at Jl.Kemang Raya no. 72 unit G, South Jakarta. For more locations visit their website www.anomalicoffee.com

You Only Live Once a.k.a YOLO is probably the motto of this generation. Est.2013, YOLO public house is an underground themed gastropub that serves amazing food and cocktails worth trying in this life! Door opens at 11 am-12 pm on Sunday until Thursday and on Friday and Saturday, it closes at 3 am. Don't miss out YOLO coz YOLO. Jl. Kemang raya no. 69E, South Jakarta

A shot of the New balance made in UK Country fair edition. Sneaker culture is rising up but great collection of sneakers are still hard to find in stores. Laffayete at Pacific place has a good collection for these classics but if you have more info, mention us @thrusociety !
The one thing you shouldn't miss out when visiting Bandung is batagor. Especially for tourists, batagor is a must try delicassy from indonesia! #RememberYourRoots

Take a closer look at the @mischiefdenim premium grade collection. The denim label from Bandung, Indonesia is affordable and has good quality dry denim material. This is a shot of their premium label 14oz dry denim.

An amazing cafe experience brought to you by @ismaya! Djournal coffee satisfies your starwars fantasies and serves good coffee. Come and try their variety of alcohol infused coffee at Cilandak Town Square (Citos) or Grand Indonesia.

Maja house is a hot venue worth going to if you are visiting Bandung. It's a bar, a restaurant and a club on weekends with great food and definetly great vibes. Probably you should have a reservation on weekends because the place is packed! Jl. Sersan Bajuri 72, Bandung
Blue Point deserve all the hype and praises it gets. The hidden paradise in Bali has a view worth millions and magnificent waves for surfers. If you visit Bali you surely must visit Blue Point.

Have you ever tried one of the first liquid nitrogen made ice cream in Indonesia before? Head out to Lin Artisan Ice Cream and try their signature "Smiley Baileys" flavour! Jl. Taman kemang 1 no. 6, South Jakarta

In the hustle and bustle of the city, Mie Naripan is one of the most reknowned noodle shop in Bandung. Famous for their Mie Ayam with pork, Mie Naripan is a place worth visiting. Jl.Naripan 108, Bandung
Need something to kick start your day? Or just a place to rest your legs in a vintage contemporary ambience? Come check out the new Society Cafe in Bandung. Jl. Trunojoyo 8,Bandung.
